<style>
    .brand-section {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 30px;
      font-family: sans-serif;
    }
    .brand-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .brand-section p {
      font-size: 2.125rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555;
      max-width: 1500px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .brand-section .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #16949c;
    }
    .brand-section .btn {
      background-color: #16949c;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
  
  <section class="brand-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Welcome to Ignitax</h2>
      <p>
        where every tax returnis handled by a <strong>U.S. Enrolled Agent</strong>. We provide specialized, contractual tax services designed to support CPA firms and tax businesses across the USA.
      </p>
      <p>When tax season hits its peak, <strong>consider our team activated</strong>. We become your seamless, on-demand extension, ready to tackle your overflow work and help you meet every deadline with confidence, not overhead. </p>
     
    </div>
  </section>
  